Dawn of the Planet of the Apes;;88;;90;;PG-13;;Ten years after simian flu wiped out much of the world's homosapiens, genetically enhanced chimpanzee Caesar (Andy Serkis) and his ever-growing band of followers have established a thriving colony just outside San Francisco in Muir Woods. Meanwhile, a small band of human survivors emerges, which forces Caesar -- as leader -- to grapple with the dual challenge of protecting his people and re-establishing a relationship with the remaining human population -- the latter being Caesar's secret wish.;;Action,Adventure,Sci-fi;;Matt Reeves;;2014;;Andy Serkis,Jason Clarke,Gary Oldman,Keri Russell,Toby Kebbell,Kodi Smit-McPhee,Kirk Acevedo,Jon Eyez,Enrique Murciano,Terry Notary,Judy Greer,Nick Thurston,Karin Konoval,Keir O'Donnell,Kevin Rankin;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dawn_of_the_planet_of_the_apes